---

## ğŸ—ï¸ Build Instructions (macOS, Windows & Linux)

CryptoEngine ships as pure Python + PyQt6, so you can build binaries using **PyInstaller**.

Ensure dependencies installed:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install pyinstaller
```

## ğŸ macOS (.app bundle)

```bash
    pyinstaller \
    --name CryptoEngine \
    --windowed \
    --icon ssh_encryptor/assets/icon.icns \
    --add-data "ssh_encryptor/assets:assets" \
    run.py
```

## ğŸªŸ Windows (.exe)

```bash
    pyinstaller ^
    --onefile ^
    --windowed ^
    --icon ssh_encryptor/assets/icon.ico ^
    --add-data "ssh_encryptor\\assets;assets" ^
    run.py
  ```

## ğŸ§ Linux (binary or AppImage)

```bash
    pyinstaller \
    --name CryptoEngine \
    --windowed \
    --icon ssh_encryptor/assets/icon.png \
    --add-data "ssh_encryptor/assets:assets" \
    run.py
  ```

